(Vieillot, 1805)
</taxonomicName>
—Hooded siskin (
<taxonomicName box="[1081,1219,1335,1360]" class="Aves" family="Fringillidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="13" pageNumber="174" phylum="Chordata" rank="family">Fringillidae</taxonomicName>
